<div class="leftblock">
	<h2>Envirochem prides itself on its ability to cater specifically to the needs of all of its corporate and individual clients, including environmental consultants nationwide!</h2>
	<p>Our customer base varies widely from one off private customers, to established clients which cover large geographical areas such as Housing Associations and City Councils.</p>
    <p>Since our incorporation in 1989, we have also built strong relationships with a number of Universities and Colleges within the southern coastal region. We also provide analytical service to many national and local contractors in the field of asbestos removal, building and demolition.</p>
    <p>The services we provide vary greatly depending on each client's requirements, but range from single bulk sample analysis to complex asbestos surveys, independent advice to ensure compliance with the Control of Asbestos Regulations (2012), and project management of remedial works if required.</p>
</div>
